Apple today <a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2025/04/what-the-clash-joins-apple-arcade-in-may-among-five-new-games/">announced</a> that five additional games will be added to the Apple Arcade library at the beginning of next month.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2020/06/apple-arcade-orange-feature.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="900" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-748620" /><br/>
Accessible through the App Store, Apple Arcade is a subscription-based service that provides access to hundreds of games across the iPhone, iPad, Mac, Apple TV, and Apple Vision Pro, all free of ads and in-app purchases. In the U.S., Apple Arcade costs &#36;6.99 per month and is bundled with other Apple services in all <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/apple-one/">Apple One plans</a>.<br/>
<br/>
The five new games coming to Apple Arcade on Thursday, May 1:<ul><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/lego-friends-heartlake-rush/id6740321198">LEGO Friends Heartlake Rush+</a> — An endless driving and racing game, in which LEGO Friends and their pets go on a colorful, fast-paced adventure.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/what-the-clash/id1668359542">WHAT THE CLASH?</a> — A multiplayer game with hundreds of silly 1v1 mini games, and Apple TV support for playing on the big screen.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/with-my-buddy/id6503326678">with My Buddy</a> — A kid-friendly simulation game where players bond with and care for virtual puppies and kittens.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/words-of-wonders-search/id6476141662">Words of Wonders: Search+</a> — A word search game.</li><br/>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/sumi-sumi-matching-puzzle/id6670519946">SUMI SUMI: Matching Puzzle+</a> — A matching game featuring popular San-X characters.</li></ul>More details about all five games are available <a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2025/04/what-the-clash-joins-apple-arcade-in-may-among-five-new-games/">on the Apple Newsroom website</a>.<div class="linkback">Tag: <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/apple-arcade/">Apple Arcade</a></div><br/>This article, &quot;<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/04/08/apple-arcade-games-coming-may-2025/">Apple Arcade Adding Five New Games Next Month</a>&quot; first appeared on <a href="https://www.macrumors.com">MacRumors.com</a><br/><br/><a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/apple-arcade-adding-five-new-games-next-month.2454944/">Discuss this article</a> in our forums<br/><br/>